# Safety net — only ship dist/, package.json, README.md.
*
!dist/**
!package.json
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!LICENSE
# Belt-and-suspenders: never publish app artifacts even if they leak into dist/
dist/hooks/**
dist/lib-entry.*
dist/routes/**
dist/router.*
dist/server.*
dist/start.*
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/favicon.ico
